title: Who Bit Beyonce??
itunes:title: Who Bit Beyonce??
description:
Tuesday 3/27 - Today on the show after news broke about Beyonce getting bit at a party, so you already know the Beyhive was on it. Moreover, we opened the phone lines to see if our listeners had any thought of who it might be. Also Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a woman that married a 100 year old tree, and yes they were from Florida yet again. Also, Kenny Burns and Fawn Weaver stopped by to speak on the history of the Jack Daniel drink and evolving the business.
